pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 50, 4, 30]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: header-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 48, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>PROOF  //  الإثبات</p>
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 90, 700, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      text: |
        <p>منصة جاهزة ومجربة</p>
      wrap: false
  - elementId: stat-row-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 170, 1160, 130]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: s1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 185, 200, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 40
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>2,587</p>
  - elementId: s1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 240, 200, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      text: |
        <p>ملف Python</p>
  - elementId: s2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [380, 185, 200, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 40
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>172</p>
  - elementId: s2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [380, 240, 200, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      text: |
        <p>نقطة API</p>
  - elementId: s3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 185, 200, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 40
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>563</p>
  - elementId: s3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 240, 200, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      text: |
        <p>اختبار تلقائي</p>
  - elementId: s4-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [940, 185, 200, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 40
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>60</p>
  - elementId: s4-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [940, 240, 200, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      text: |
        <p>خط CI/CD</p>
  - elementId: feature-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 340, 600, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>مميزات تم اختبارها وجاهزة للاستخدام:</p>
  - elementId: checklist
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 390, 560, 280]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.8
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  CRM عقاري متكامل مع تتبع العملاء</p>
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  تحليلات السوق العقاري بالذكاء الاصطناعي</p>
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  إدارة المشاريع والوحدات</p>
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  تواصل ذكي عبر WhatsApp والبريد</p>
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  امتثال كامل لـ PDPL وZATCA</p>
        <p><span style="color:#1B5E3B;">✓</span>  بوابة دفع Moyasar متكاملة</p>
  - elementId: badge-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [700, 390, 520, 280]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: badge-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [910, 420, 64, 64]
    iconName: shield-check
    color: "$primary"
  - elementId: badge-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [730, 500, 460, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      align: center
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>منصة جاهزة للبيع اليوم</p>
  - elementId: badge-sub
    elementType: text
    bounds: [730, 550, 460, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: center
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>ابدأ بالتشخيص المجاني واكتشف كيف تساعدك Dealix</p>
